## 🚀 Getting Started
### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```sh
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/mind-matrix.git
cd mind-matrix
```

### 2️⃣ Install Dependencies
```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3️⃣ Run Mind Matrix
```sh
python mind_matrix.py
```

